{"tid":509475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【追蹤聖誕老人】特朗普夫婦客串接線生 答小朋友電話","createTime":"2017-12-25T11:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T12:15:40.000Z","uid":84436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"720713346b9c71e52c8881b1f4c62947726a4dd8","tid":509475,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171225/57624042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F57624042&d=ZOOWPitwjGLyUMxvqtd0s5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=3e4e0b78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F57624042&h=5365605e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171225/57624042</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍北美航空航天司令部（NORAD）按傳統「追蹤」聖誕老人行蹤，並向致電熱線的大小朋友講解聖誕老人跑了去何處，總統特朗普和第一夫人梅拉尼婭（Melania Trump）亦在平安夜親自接聽熱線，跟小朋友聊天。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在佛羅里達州私人大宅馬阿拉歌莊園（Mar-a-Lago）歡度聖誕，並與梅拉尼婭在佈置有巨型聖誕樹的大廳接聽熱線。特朗普跟一名名叫卡斯珀(Casper)的小孩通話︰「你最想要甚麼？積木(Building blocks)！」這位地產大亨隨即說︰「我也喜歡積木。我想聖誕老人會給你很多積木，多到你用不完。」<br />\n另一名小孩卻不想要玩具，只聽到特朗普說︰「所以你希望祖母出院？這是你的願望？很好，這比要求玩具或甚麼要棒。你祖母會好起來的，好嗎？她會好起來。」他又邀另一名小孩到華盛頓時可跟他見面。<br />\n特朗普共接聽了11名小孩的電話，梅拉尼婭則接聽了10名小孩的電話，她向其中一人確認聖誕老人正前來，「你上床睡覺，聖誕老人才會來」。<br />\n公眾可以致電或上網追蹤聖誕老人行蹤。NORAD追蹤聖誕老人的傳統，由1955年開始。那年，科羅拉多州一份報章刊登一條聖誕熱線，豈料印錯電話號碼駁到NORAD，NORAD錯有錯着，委派職員或義工回答關於聖誕老人的問題"},{"pid":"403e7631c259daeeab59df35f35a2002b8ad5092","tid":509475,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"好溫馨"},{"pid":"46ed5983a916da651e80c3547ea9ed4460f4640e","tid":509475,"uid":125357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"我想聖誕老人送金仔個人頭畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47684c21c75bf0661b613144d02be73d4f03d5bc","tid":509475,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403e7631c259daeeab59df35f35a2002b8ad5092","tid":509475,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"好溫馨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"普世價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882c8d053f913b71dbec54a149df09d3c8d41d74","tid":509475,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uxf1lEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fuxf1lEi.jpg&h=aacdd95b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87ac07b4a38a693cb7c11dc8355dde489c13a57f","tid":509475,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T12:15:40.000Z","msg":"叫ivanka trump聽我電話"}]}